### SportsApiPro - player by playerId
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/player?playerId=123

### SportsApiPro - all players by teamId
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/team-players?teamId=8650

### SportsApiPro - athlete basic by athleteId
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/athlete-basic?athleteId=868&fullDetails=false

### SportsApiPro - allowed leagues (47,112,87,55,53,54)
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/leagues

### SportsApiPro - teams by leagueId
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/teams?leagueId=112

### SportsApiPro - team detail by teamId
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/team-detail?teamId=8650

### SportsApiPro - teams by sportId and competitionId
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/competition-teams?sportId=1&competitionId=72

### SportsApiPro - latest matchday ratings by sportId and competitionId
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/latest-matchday-ratings?sportId=1&competitionId=72

### SportsApiPro - collect fixture event refs (ids + metadata)
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/fixture/event-refs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "config": {
    "competitionId": 72,
    "seasonNum": 228,
    "stageNum": 3,
    "teams": [
      { "id": 9050, "name": "Boca Juniors" },
      { "id": 9051, "name": "River Plate" }
    ]
  },
  "options": {
    "maxPagesPerTeam": 80,
    "sleepMsBetweenRequests": 200
  }
}

### SportsApiPro - build fixture from event refs
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/fixture/build
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventRefs": [
    {
      "gameId": 123456,
      "competitionId": 72,
      "seasonNum": 228,
      "stageNum": 3,
      "homeCompetitorId": 9050,
      "awayCompetitorId": 9051,
      "startTime": "2026-02-10T21:00:00Z",
      "statusGroup": 1,
      "statusText": "Scheduled",
      "source": "fixtures"
    }
  ],
  "options": {
    "sleepMsBetweenRequests": 0
  }
}


### SportsApiPro - build fixture completo por competencia
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/fixture/build-competition
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sportId": 1,
  "competitionId": 72
}

### SportsApiPro - rankings mapeados a playerPerformance local
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/sportsapipro/rankings/player-performances?sportId=1&competitionId=72
